- Continuing development of best management practices under OSHA's Voluntary Protection Program;



- Conduct a third-party audit of our Process Safety Management system;



- Continue using safety risk assessment tools in an effort to reduce human error leading to a workplace injury or an accidental release;



- Continuing an employee exposure monitoring program for acrylonitrile;



- Continuing on-site emergency responder drills; and,



